data.description: Charming 4 Bedroom, 2 Bath Brick-Faced Home in the Tranquil Neighborhood of Quail Hollow  This 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom brick-faced gem offers 1,744 square feet of comfortable living space in a peaceful neighborhood. This property is perfect for anyone seeking a place to call home. Enjoy the luxury of four spacious bedrooms, each offering plenty closet space. These versatile rooms can accommodate your needs, whether you need a guest room, home office, or playroom.  The two well-appointed bathrooms provide convenience and functionality. The primary ensuite features modern fixtures and a relaxing ambiance with a separate water closet, double vanity sinks, brushed nickel fixtures.  Semi-open floor concept creates an ideal space for gatherings, entertaining, and daily living. The kitchen seamlessly flows into the dining and living areas, making it easy to stay connected. The fenced yard is perfect for entertaining, pets, and outdoor enthusiasts. It offers both privacy and security while allowing you to enjoy the outdoors in peace. Nestled in a peaceful and friendly neighborhood, this home provides a serene setting for a comfortable life. Enjoy tranquil evenings and a strong sense of community. Experience the convenience of easy access to shopping, dining, and entertainment options. You're just minutes away from everything you need. Beach lovers will appreciate the short 20-minute drive to Flagler Beach, where you can soak up the sun, swim in the ocean, and enjoy all the coastal amenities.  Don't miss this opportunity to make this fantastic property your forever home in this quiet neighborhood and proximity to Flagler Beach. Schedule a viewing today and imagine the possibilities of life in this charming brick-faced home. Schedule your showing TODAY!
